subject: late to the party
body: i'm thankful for the kacey musgraves song "[late to the party](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JM07F5bYRhc)," which like miguel's "[do you...](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-BW2gKnVz8)" is a song i think of as one of "our songs" and i'm thankful that last night when d and i were jamming, she picked it out of the list of songs in her guitar tabs app and we played [a loose, sped-up version](https://drive.google.com/file/d/18DkJLHc0lW9h6kmeTX-0IRTZzz2sIr9x/view?usp=sharing).
